snippet: Law enforcement officials said they found the body of a man suspected of shooting a ranger at Mount Rainier National Park on Sunday morning
abstract: Law enforcement agencies say they found the body of Benjamin Colton Barnes, man suspected of killing Mount Rainier National Park Ranger Margaret Anderson.

byline.original: By WILLIAM YARDLEY and ISOLDE RAFTERY
byline.contributor: William Yardley reported from Mount Rainier National Park, and Isolde Raftery from Seattle.

lead_paragraph: Law enforcement officials said they found the body of a man suspected of shooting a ranger at Mount Rainier National Park on Sunday morning

headline.seo: Body Found at Mt. Rainier Belongs to Ranger Shooting Suspect
headline.main: Man Believed to Have Killed Park Ranger Is Found Dead
headline.print_headline: Man Believed to Have Killed Park Ranger Is Found Dead
